  "caveats": [
    "Bundle was compiled before the observed-rainfall override hook in core/dps_engine.py:L112-129 ran for these storms. The override would replace rain_result.estimated_total_mm with the ground_truth value at compile time. Once the bundle is recompiled, the bias measured here disappears for storms with ground_truth entries \u2014 but the underlying estimator (used for storms without ground_truth) still has the systematic over-estimation problem documented here.",
    "Five EP storms in ground_truth (Patricia, Lane, Otis, Hilary, John) aren't in the compiled bundle yet, so they can't be cross-checked against an engine estimate. Documented in EP_DPS_AUDIT.md followup #1."
  ]
